Whether it’s the weather, your business, relationship, finances, health, productivity, etc it’s all about the quality of the training that you decide to put yourself into and the DISCIPLINE/self-Love you step into in order to achieve the highest possible result. 

For today, right now at 108°.......
I decided to get outside at 6:15am when it was 73°. There’s working hard and then there’s working smart. 

I used to limit my potential by retelling & boxing myself into my old story that “I was a night owl” 🌟 🦉

